  "texts": [
    "There were 998 duplicates removed using automatic screening by Covidence along with manual screening between data extractors (Y-J.P., A.P., J.D.",
    "), and 3,126 titles and abstracts were screened.",
    "Quality and rigor of extractions were maintained via (i) standardization of extractions based on an example provided by consensus amongst the authors, (ii) duplicate screenings and confirmations of each extraction.",
    "Based on our criteria, 63 articles were eligible for full-text screening, of which 8 were excluded given that their topics did not align with the inclusion criteria.",
    "55 articles were ultimately included."
  ],
